juniES2Registry.name: juniES2Registry

revisions.description: renamed entity objects, reordered to match rsSystem.mi2 and removed obsoleted boards.
Updated for second generation E-series hardware.
Renamed E2 MIB objects to ES2 MIB objects.
Initial version of this SNMP management information module.

juniES2Registry.contactinfo: Juniper Networks, Inc. Postal: 10 Technology Park Drive Westford, MA 01886-3146 USA Tel: +1 978 589 5800 Email: mib@Juniper.net
juniES2Registry.description: Juniper second generation E-series product family system-specific object identification values. This module defines AutonomousType (OID) values for all the physical entity types (entPhysicalVendorType). This module will be updated whenever a new type of module or other hardware becomes available in second generation E-series systems.

es2Chassis.name: es2Chassis
es2Chassis.description: The vendor type ID for a second generation E-series chassis. This identifies an 'overall' physical entity for any second generation E-series system.

e320BaseChassis.name: e320BaseChassis
e320BaseChassis.description: E320 base chassis with 12 slots for line modules - includes chassis, midplane, DC PDU, and fan tray. The E320 system uses a carrier-class design with a passive midplane, active front-insert line modules(LM) and rear-insert input/output adapters(IOA).

e120BaseChassis.name: e120BaseChassis
e120BaseChassis.description: E120 base chassis with 6 slots for line modules - includes chassis, midplane, DC PDU, and fan tray. The E120 system uses a carrier-class design with a passive midplane, active front-insert line modules(LM) and rear-insert input/output adapters(IOA).

es2FanAssembly.name: es2FanAssembly
es2FanAssembly.description: The vendor type ID for a second generation E-series fan assembly.

es2PowerInput.name: es2PowerInput
es2PowerInput.description: The vendor type ID for a second generation E-series power distribution module.

es2Midplane.name: es2Midplane
es2Midplane.description: The vendor type ID for a second generation E-series midplane.

es2SrpModule.name: es2SrpModule
es2SrpModule.description: The vendor type ID for a second generation E-series system controller/ switch fabric module.

e320Srp100.name: e320Srp100
e320Srp100.description: E320 100Gb SRP - The Switch Route Processor (SRP) is responsible for running the routing protocols as well as overall system control. The SRP also contains a switch fabric slice that is responsible for packet forwarding.

e320Srp320.name: e320Srp320
e320Srp320.description: E320 320Gb SRP - The Switch Route Processor (SRP) is responsible for running the routing protocols as well as overall system control. The SRP also contains a switch fabric slice that is responsible for packet forwarding.

e120Srp120.name: e120Srp120
e120Srp120.description: E120 120Gb SRP - The Switch Route Processor (SRP) is responsible for running the routing protocols as well as overall system control. The SRP also contains a switch fabric slice that is responsible for packet forwarding.

es2SwitchFabricModule.name: es2SwitchFabricModule
es2SwitchFabricModule.description: The vendor type ID for a second generation E-series switch fabric module.

e320Sfm100.name: e320Sfm100
e320Sfm100.description: E320 100Gb switch fabric module. The SFM functions include buffer management, queuing, scheduling and packet processing.

e320Sfm320.name: e320Sfm320
e320Sfm320.description: E320 320Gb switch fabric module. The SFM functions include buffer management, queuing, scheduling and packet processing.

e120Sfm120.name: e120Sfm120
e120Sfm120.description: E120 120Gb switch fabric module. The SFM functions include buffer management, queuing, scheduling and packet processing.

es2SrpIoa.name: es2SrpIoa
es2SrpIoa.description: The vendor type ID for the system controller I/O adapter for a second generation E-series system.

e320SrpIoa.name: e320SrpIoa
e320SrpIoa.description: E320 SRP IOA. This card provides clocking functions as well as management and alarm interfaces.

es2ForwardingModule.name: es2ForwardingModule
es2ForwardingModule.description: The vendor type ID for a second generation E-series forwarding module.

es2Lm4.name: es2Lm4
es2Lm4.description: E320 4Gb (series 1) line module. This Line Module supports both uplink and customer facing IOAs and is responsible for processing data traffic.

es2Lm10Uplink.name: es2Lm10Uplink
es2Lm10Uplink.description: E320 10Gb (series 2) uplink line module. This Line Module is primarily focused on uplink IOAs and is responsible for processing data traffic.

es2Lm10.name: es2Lm10
es2Lm10.description: E320 10Gb (series 3) line module. This Line Module supports both uplink and customer facing IOAs and is responsible for processing data traffic.

es2Lm10s.name: es2Lm10s
es2Lm10s.description: E320 10Gb (series 4) line module. This Line Module supports both uplink and customer facing IOAs and is responsible for processing data traffic.

es2ForwardingIoa.name: es2ForwardingIoa
es2ForwardingIoa.description: The vendor type ID for a second generation E-series I/O adapter for a forwarding module.

es2Ge4S1Ioa.name: es2Ge4S1Ioa
es2Ge4S1Ioa.description: E320 GE-4 IOA. This is a series 1, half-height, single wide IOA with 4 physical interfaces that require pluggable GE interfaces. This IOA uses the full capacity of a Series 1 line module.

es2Oc48Stm16PosS1Ioa.name: es2Oc48Stm16PosS1Ioa
es2Oc48Stm16PosS1Ioa.description: E320 OC48/STM16 POS IOA. This is a series 1, half-height, single wide IOA with 1 physical interface that requires a pluggable OC48/STM16 interface.

es2ServiceS1Ioa.name: es2ServiceS1Ioa
es2ServiceS1Ioa.description: E320 service IOA. This is a series 1, full-height, single wide IOA and does not support any physical interfaces.

es2Oc3Stm1x8AtmS1Ioa.name: es2Oc3Stm1x8AtmS1Ioa
es2Oc3Stm1x8AtmS1Ioa.description: E320 OC3/STM1-8 ATM IOA. This is a series 1, half-height, single wide IOA that supports 8 physical interfaces that require pluggable OC3/STM1 interfaces. This IOA can be combined with other half-height IOAs (except those that use the full capacity of a slot's bandwidth such as the GE-4 IOA).

es2RedundancyS1Ioa.name: es2RedundancyS1Ioa
es2RedundancyS1Ioa.description: E320 redundancy IOA. This is a series 1, full-height, single wide IOA and does not support any physical interfaces.

es2Oc12Stm4x2PosS1Ioa.name: es2Oc12Stm4x2PosS1Ioa
es2Oc12Stm4x2PosS1Ioa.description: E320 OC12/STM4-2 POS IOA. This is a series 1, half-height, single wide IOA that supports 2 physical interfaces that require pluggable OC12/STM4 interfaces. This IOA can be combined with other half-height IOAs (except those that use the full capacity of a slot's bandwidth such as the GE-4 IOA).

es2Oc12Stm4x2AtmS1Ioa.name: es2Oc12Stm4x2AtmS1Ioa
es2Oc12Stm4x2AtmS1Ioa.description: E320 OC12/STM4-2 ATM IOA. This is a series 1, half-height, single wide IOA that supports 2 physical interfaces that require pluggable OC12/STM4 interfaces. This IOA can be combined with other half-height IOAs (except those that use the full capacity of a slot's bandwidth such as the GE-4 IOA).

es2dash10GeS1Ioa.name: es2dash10GeS1Ioa
es2dash10GeS1Ioa.description: E320 10GE IOA. This is a series 1, full-height, single wide IOA that supports 2 physical interface that requires a pluggable 10GE interface.

es2Ge8S1Ioa.name: es2Ge8S1Ioa
es2Ge8S1Ioa.description: E320 GE-8 IOA. This is a series 1, half-height, single wide IOA that supports 8 physical interfaces that require pluggable GE transceivers. This IOA will support a configuration of 8 active or 4 active + 4 standby interfaces.

es2dash10GePrS2Ioa.name: es2dash10GePrS2Ioa
es2dash10GePrS2Ioa.description: E320 10GE IOA with port redundancy (PR). This is a series 2, full-height, single wide IOA that supports 2 physical interfaces (1 active + 1 standby) that require pluggable 10GE transceivers.

es2Ge20S2Ioa.name: es2Ge20S2Ioa
es2Ge20S2Ioa.description: E320 GE-20 IOA. This is a series 2, full-height, single wide IOA that supports 20 physical interfaces that require pluggable GE transceivers. This IOA will support a configuration of 20 active or 10 active + 10 standby interfaces.
